protected high performance storage.

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:23.870
And also when you look at
things like XSAN introduced,

00:02:23.870 --> 00:02:27.160
be shipping this fall,
bringing a SAN file system to

00:02:27.160 --> 00:02:31.800
Mac OS X with really excellent
storage and shared storage capability.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:35.230
