00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:59.610
And so we see customer
adoption really taking off,

00:02:59.930 --> 00:03:02.710
especially with the Xserve
G5 bringing this power and

00:03:02.710 --> 00:03:04.840
technology into the form factor.

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:09.980
